column1: Bilateral Remittance Estimates for 2014 using Migrant Stocks, Host Country Incomes, and Origin Country Incomes (millions of US$) (April 2015 Version)

These estimates are based on the methodology developed by Ratha and Shaw, 2007, "South-South Migration and Remittances," Development Prospects Group, World Bank (www.worldbank.org/prospects/migrationandremittances). The remittance data is for 2014, disaggregated using host country and origin country incomes, and estimated migrant stocks from 2013.
These estimates are based on the Migration and Remittances Factbook 2015, which includes new bilateral data on migration stocks", World Bank (www.worldbank.org/prospects/migrationandremittances).
